title: Eurovision Song Contest Final 2014 HDTV x264-GTi mp4
description: Graham Norton introduces and commentates on the 59th Eurovision Song Contest live from Copenhagen. Singer-songwriter Molly Smitten-Downes flies the flag for the United Kingdom in the Eurovision Song Contest in Copenhagen, Denmark. Molly performs her self-penned song Children of the Universe and is one of 26 acts competing for the coveted title of Eurovision Song Contest winner 2014.A Big Thank You to Helen aka Gti for doing this in HD
